  "title": "Contract Project Management !! #HYNT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong><br /></p><ul><li><p>Plan, manage, and execute manufacturing-related projects from initiation through completion</p></li><li><p>Develop and maintain project plans, schedules, budgets, and risk registers</p></li><li><p>Coordinate cross-functional teams including engineering, production, quality, validation, EHS, procurement, and external contractors</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with GMP, FDA, EMA, ICH, and other applicable regulatory and quality requirements</p></li><li><p>Monitor project progress, identify risks or issues, and implement mitigation strategies</p></li><li><p>Manage change control, documentation, and project reporting in accordance with site procedures</p></li><li><p>Facilitate project meetings, track action items, and communicate status to stakeholders and leadership</p></li><li><p>Support equipment installation, process scale-up, technology transfer, facility upgrades, or continuous improvement initiatives</p></li><li><p>Ensure health, safety, and environmental requirements are integrated into project execution<br /><br /><a href=\"https://employer.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/jobs/contract-finance-executive-hynt-recruit-express-4b362a49692dfbac3e98a5394fa8f6f4/view#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Please send your resume to rehealth@recruitexpress.com.sg.</a></p><p>We regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>Chloe Impens| Outsourcing Team<br />EA License Number: 99C4599<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd | Company Reg. No. 199601303W</p></li></ul>",
